  <summary>4/8/1997--Introduced.
Corporate Welfare Reduction Act - Establishes an independent Corporate Welfare Reduction Commission to recommend reductions in corporate subsidies to reduce the Federal budget deficit. Establishes in the Congress a Joint Committee on Corporate Subsidy Reduction. Sets forth requirements for congressional consideration of Commission reports.</summary>
